    "description": "你好探险家！<br>我是蒂姆·埃杰尔教授，我是时间机器的发明者，也是狂热的猫迷！不幸的是，我遇到一个问题，也许你可以帮助我。<br>你看，我心爱的猫不见了。在实验室玩耍时，它们激活了我的时间机器和⚡瞬移⚡，现在他们迷失在了空间和时间中！你需要从古埃及出发，一直来到20世纪末的纽约街道，甚至超越现在到达未来的东京。<br>你的目标是找到所有的猫！请注意，这些猫真的很擅长躲藏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >😺可爱的猫</h2>拯救超过290只藏在最不寻常之处的猫。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599880/extras/8e816724d642b3def9aa005f81f84d68.poster.avif?t=1724666519\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599880/extras/8e816724d642b3def9aa005f81f84d68.webm?t=1724666519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599880/extras/8e816724d642b3def9aa005f81f84d68.mp4?t=1724666519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧩触觉谜题</h2>解决惊人的拼图和谜题，以拯救所有被困的猫。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599880/extras/f1fe8b5f57a2751d90fc663694f43ac2.poster.avif?t=1724666519\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599880/extras/f1fe8b5f57a2751d90fc663694f43ac2.webm?t=1724666519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599880/extras/f1fe8b5f57a2751d90fc663694f43ac2.mp4?t=1724666519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⭐️️制作精美的3D关卡</h2>逃到不同年代的留六个独特地点。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599880/extras/e4324542171e25e6c8d53e70348f0cf6.poster.avif?t=1724666519\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599880/extras/e4324542171e25e6c8d53e70348f0cf6.webm?t=1724666519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1599880/extras/e4324542171e25e6c8d53e70348f0cf6.mp4?t=1724666519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎶放松的音乐</h2>在探索时聆听这一年代的轻松声音。<br><br>花点时间，享受这段旅程吧！<br>蒂姆.E教授",
